  <emu-note>
    <p>There are 253 available named character references total.</p>
    <p>Among these, 252 are those listed by <a href="https://www.w3.org/TR/1999/REC-html401-19991224/sgml/entities.html">HTML 4.01 Specification</a>. The remaining one is `&amp;amp;apos;` for ASCII single quote.</p>
    <p>Those that were later added in <a href="https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/named-characters.html">HTML Living Standard</a>, except for `&amp;amp;apos;`, are not included.</p>
  </emu-note>
  <emu-annex id="sec-jsx-named-character-references-static-semantics-sv">
